data.description: This home is a rare find! Sit and relax on your rocking chair front porch and enjoy a private oasis in the Ola School District. Charming ranch situated on private 2.0-acrelot; this 4-bedroom 2 bath home has an unfinished basement with many possibilities. Situated in a great location this home is 20 minutes or less from downtown Mcdonough, Covington and Jackson. Only 30 minutes to Stockbridge, Conyers and Monticello. Sellers are leaving batting cage!
